{"id":161352,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/联合早报-携带上车的物件不得超越限定尺寸/","date":"2011-06-15T13:01:02Z","modified":"2011-06-15T13:01:02Z","title":"联合早报 | 携带上车的物件不得超越限定尺寸","content":"<div>\n<p>携带上车的物件不得超越限定尺寸</p>\n<p>（2011-06-15）</p>\n<table align=\"left\" width=\"306\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n早报导读</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/wapzb.shtml\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"250\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zaobao.com/ssi/bizp/svc/wap300_110421.gif\" /></a></p>\n<table width=\"300\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/face2face/face2face.shtml\">[人物面对面]</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/face2face/pages1/face2face110615.shtml\">赌管局局长拉惹古玛卸任前夕专访</a><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/china/cnpol/cnpol.shtml\">[中国政情]</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/china/cnpol/pages4/cnpol110615d.shtml\">中国崛起与中国外交原则的困境</a><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/hotspot/taiwan_food.shtml\">[塑化剂风波]</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/hotspot/pages/hotspot110615a.shtml\">我国当局：确保食品药品等的安全</a><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/china/zaodian/zaodian.shtml\">[中国早点]</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/china/zaodian/pages2/zaodian_shanghai110615.shtml\">教育偏差应积极面对</a></p>\n<table width=\"300\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/services/pages/recruitment_110208a.html\"><strong>联合早报网招聘 Freelance网络新闻编辑</strong></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> 谨答复《联合早报·交流站》于6月9日刊登的郑秀凤读者投函《为何乘地铁不能携带电视机？》：</p>\n<p> “快捷交通系统条例”（Rapid Transit Systems Regulations）规定，过于笨重庞大的物品是不能携带上地铁列车的。条规容许携带上车的行李或其他物品，其大小不得超过81cm x 58cm x 30cm。另外，在上午9时30分至下午4时以及晚上8时至列车运行时间终止的两个时段里，折叠式脚踏车在折叠后的尺寸如果小于114cm x 64cm x 36cm也可携带上车。</p>\n<p> 我们在各地铁站的车资扫描闸门处都有放置通告，告知乘客关于携带上车的大件物品的尺寸限制，并在墙上及地上设有测量尺寸的标线，让乘客可在进闸门前测量要携带上车的物件，确保它们符合规定。</p>\n<p>SMRT企业有限公司</p>\n<p>企业推展与通讯高级执行员</p>\n<p>张玉莲</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/06/bd600b9dtrack.gif\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/06/14df7b52EKCgBk8MZdE.gif.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com%2Fyl%2Fyl110615_005.shtml&#038;title=%E6%90%BA%E5%B8%A6%E4%B8%8A%E8%BD%A6%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E8%B6%85%E8%B6%8A%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/06/9e5092b2p300_110421.gif-150x150.gif\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":699,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}